{"tid":1800570,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"9月黨鐵東鐵綫在紅磡出軌的意外  機電署初步排除是由外物或惡意破壞所致","createTime":"2019-12-28T03:11:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-28T05:14:06.000Z","uid":41818,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"fd277d95c0a28334da80f631a3a9c8f4d7308918","tid":1800570,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T03:11:36.000Z","msg":"【有線新聞】9月港鐵東鐵綫列車在紅磡出軌的意外，機電署初步排除是由外物或惡意破壞所致。<br />\n<br />\n事發在9月17日早上，一列東鐵綫列車駛至紅磡站時突然出軌，造成八人受傷。機電署事後發現路軌有一條約1至2毫米裂紋，<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">調查後初步已排除事故是由外物或惡意破壞所致</span></strong>，預計2月底前完成調查工作。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/14067\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F14067&d=CRZj9ITMXIzKHLmvffUzPM2proQWM4oxojYLcFbEfDU%3D&h=557c3da9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F14067&h=7a5a53c7\" target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/14067</a>"},{"pid":"be51196e203d358eafd62a191d2b970fe0c38b9e","tid":1800570,"uid":272531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T03:22:13.000Z","msg":"「黃色經濟圈」認證要大家幫手 - 籌款箱計劃<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1800571\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1800571</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"eb1e5250557274a99a09a7481138e993e08b3e0b","tid":1800570,"uid":72185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T03:45:37.000Z","msg":"咁一定係關佔中事"},{"pid":"38b204387909eac7f5c096c5d46be5eb83777701","tid":1800570,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eb1e5250557274a99a09a7481138e993e08b3e0b","tid":1800570,"uid":72185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T03:45:37.000Z","msg":"咁一定係關佔中事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T03:46:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd42b679ce204cd37f7f46a7a291f97e4c7